\f1\b0\fs48 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}6 brats, sliced into thirds (about 2-inch pieces)\
{\listtext	\'95	}8 slices lean, good quality smoky bacon\
{\listtext	\'95	}Extra-virgin olive oil, for drizzling\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 (16 to 18-ounce) cans good quality baked beans\
