{\listtext	\'95	}1 large shallot, finely chopped\
{\listtext	\'95	}Coarse black pepper\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/4 cup Worcestershire sauce or steak sauce (recommended: Lea and Perrin's thick Worcestershire Sauce)\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 red chile peppers\
{\listtext	\'95	}Small bunch thin scallions, whites and greens thinly sliced on an angle\
